Processors 
Processors must keep a record containing a minimum of the following information (Art. 12 para. 
3 FADP): 
- 
the identity of the processor; 
- 
the identity of the data controller; 
- 
the categories of processing carried out on behalf of the controller; 
- 
as far as possible, a general description of the measures taken to guarantee data 
security in accordance with Article 8 FADP; 
- 
if the data are to be disclosed abroad, the name of the country concerned and the 
safeguards taken (Art. 16 para. 2 FADP), as detailed in the section on disclosure of 
data abroad;
